window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Framed in the doorway of Poirot's bedroom stood an uninvited guest, coated from head to foot in dust. The man's gaunt face stared for a moment, then he swayed and fell. </p><p>Who was he? Was he suffering from shock or just exhaustion? Above all, what was the significance of the figure four, scribbled over and over again on a sheet of paper? </p><p>Poirot finds himself plunged into a world of international intrigue, risking his life to uncover the truth about <i>Number Four</i>.</p>"; 
